State of North Carolina
v.
Kenneth E. Robinson No. 200P07-5 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 Kenneth E. Robinson, for Robinson, Kenneth E. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Valerie Mitchell Asbell, District Attorney, for State of NC. Grady L. Balentine, Jr., Special Deputy Attorney General.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 29th of June 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Halifax County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
